title Promo Tile Generation Flow

|Script Initialization|
start
:Resolve file paths\n(ROOT, OUT = extension/icons/promo-small.png);
:Define brand color constants\nBG '#0e0d10' · BG_TOP '#161318'\nMAGENTA '#cc1b89' · TEXT '#f5f3ef' · TEXT_DIM '#7a7680';

|SVG Construction|
:Build inline SVG template literal\n(renderTile — 440×280 px);
note right
  Visual layers composed:
  • Background rect — vertical linear gradient (BG_TOP → BG)
  • Subtle grid texture (opacity 0.04)
  • linearGradients: bg, slop
  • radialGradient: cardGlow
  • feGaussianBlur filter: softShadow
end note
:Compose brand wordmark group\n(icon rect + slash line + "Impeccable" text @ x=28,y=26);
:Compose DEVTOOLS badge group\n(pill rect + label text @ x=338,y=28);
:Compose demo UI card group\n(shadow rect + glow overlay + sparkle emojis\n+ gradient headline "AI-Powered Magic"\n+ magenta outline path + label tab);
:Compose bottom taglines\n("Detect AI slop in any web page." y=244\n"24 detections · Open DevTools…" y=262);
:Wrap SVG in minimal HTML\n(body 440×280, margin/padding reset, overflow hidden);

|Puppeteer Renderer|
:Launch headless Chromium\npuppeteer.launch({ headless: true });
:Open new browser page\nbrowser.newPage();
:Set viewport\n{ width: 440, height: 280, deviceScaleFactor: 1 };
:Inject HTML + SVG content\npage.setContent(html);
:Capture screenshot\npage.screenshot({ path: OUT, omitBackground: false });

|Script Initialization|
:Close headless browser\nbrowser.close();
:Log completion\nconsole.log("Generated extension/icons/promo-small.png");
stop

@enduml
